            {
                "drawing_id": "eeb47e69-f380-4c01-aab7-d0877e677c12",
                "locked": false,
                "rotation": 0,
                "svg": "<svg width=\"508\" height=\"206\"><text font-family=\"TypeWriter\" font-size=\"10.0\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#000000\" fill-opacity=\"1.0\">K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n:\n- Sau khi b\u1eadt t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 switch, SW1 --&gt; root\n- Tr\u00ean m\u00e1y t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ea1y script python v\u1edbi th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n \nscapy g\u1eedi g\u00f3i tin c\u00f3 prio nh\u1ecf (b\u1eb1ng 0)\n--&gt; M\u00e1y kali tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh root\n--&gt; C\u00e1c g\u00f3i tin l\u00fac n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111i qua root \n- Tr\u00ean 2 m\u00e1y n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n telnet v\u1edbi nhau\n- Tr\u00ean m\u00e1y t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng wireshark c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3i tin\n\n- Sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tool yersinia \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n dos, g\u1eedi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eedi TCN\nl\u00e0m SW li\u00ean t\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 x\u00f3a b\u1ea3ng --&gt; qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i cpu</text></svg>",
                "x": 262,
                "y": 7,
                "z": 2
            },
